DEMO
====
demo.cpp is a wandering pixel


VNC CLIENT
==========
vnc.cpp is a VNC client.
As parameters it requires 'ip-address port-number password' (where password is optional if the VNC server is not requesting it).


configuration example
---------------------
descr = "my plugin source";
type = "plugin";
source-plugin-file = "source-plugins/vnc.so.0.1";
source-plugin-parameter = "192.168.1.100 5901 mypassword";

